trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Contém uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> .

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection> class allows you to programmatically access a collection of <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping> objects.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection> classe permite que você acessar programaticamente uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping> objetos.

trans-unit.source: The collection can be accessed with either the key or the index.
trans-unit.target: A coleção pode ser acessada com a chave ou o índice.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the virtual directory path.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que contém o caminho do diretório virtual.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> object to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona um objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> à instância <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="mapping" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="mapping" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="virtualDirectory" /> already exists in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: A <paramref name="virtualDirectory" /> já existe em <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> é somente leitura.

trans-unit.source: Returns a string array that contains all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna uma matriz de cadeia de caracteres que contém todas as chaves na instância <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A string array that contains all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz de cadeia de caracteres que contém todas as chaves na <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instância.

trans-unit.source: Clears all <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> objects from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Limpa todos os objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> da instância <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional que é o destino dos elementos copiados do <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Array" /> deve ter indexação com base em zero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero na <c>array</c> na qual a cópia começa.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> collection to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia toda a coleção <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMappingCollection" /> para um <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional compatível, começando no índice especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> property of <paramref name="array" /> is less than the value of <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> plus <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.Array.Length" /> de <paramref name="array" /> é menor que o valor de <see cref="P:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.Count" /> mais <paramref name="index" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> collection element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o elemento da coleção <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.VirtualDirectoryMapping" /> especificado.
